N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 659.5 - Analytical procedure

State Regulations

Analysis to determine the total phosphorus content of a
household cleansing product shall be performed in accordance with methods and
procedures approved by the commissioner. Notes
